ht:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2、在教务管理系统中对</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2026届</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各专业（方向）教学计划进行维护（核对、修改）。</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院(系)、计划科</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="108"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">10.11-10.14</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="88"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">设置教务管理系统机审毕业标准</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="369"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">1、根据执行计划确认并在教务系统中设置教学执行计划中的毕业标准；</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2、通过核对执行计划与毕业班学生修读树，发现、落实并解决相关问题，确保机审毕业标准准确无误。</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院(系)、计划科</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="108"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">10.15-10.20</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="88"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">落实毕业生学分认定情况</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="369"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">1、汇总并整理境内境外交流、转专业、降级以及因综合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">培养方案</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">调整等原因需要进行学分认定的毕业班学生的学分认定表，同时严格按照《校外学分、学位认定实施办法》、《校内学分认定实施办法》进行审核；</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2、落实以上认定表信息是否在教务管理系统中已完成学分认定操作。</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院(系)、教务科、合作与交流科</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="108"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">10.21-10.25</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="88"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">系统毕业资格预审核</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="369"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">在教务管理系统完成毕业资格预审核（机审），生成预审核结果，填写附件3《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2026届</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">本科毕业班学生毕业资格预审核明细表》</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院(系)、教务科</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="108"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">10.26-10.31</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="88"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">组织核对不通过、缺漏课程的处理情况</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="369"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">1、各院（系）根据预审核结果和学生成绩总表，填写附件4《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2026届</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">本科毕业班学生毕业资格审查预审不通过课程处理汇总表》，确保不遗漏学生，不缺漏课程（含通识课）；</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2、组织毕业班学生核对汇总表中不通过课程、缺漏课程的处理情况。</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院（系）</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="108"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">11.1-11.6</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="88"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">组织毕业班学生补选课</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="369"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">1、组织毕业班学生根据预审结果进行补选课；</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">2、做好毕业班学生补选课的跟进和</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">学业提升</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">工作；</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">3、上交附件2-4材料。</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-top: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext;" valign="center" width="92"><p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:30px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:16px">各院（系）</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:43px;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">填写附件2-4，并于</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">11月6日17：00前</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">上交教务科/国际校区教学事务办公室(五山校区</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">本科生院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">教务科笃行楼北座301黄老师；大学城校区图书馆一楼教务科凌老师；广州国际校区教学事务办公室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">F1-a213</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">黄老师)。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">电子版统一发至</span><a href="mailto:zmling@scut.edu.cn"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);font-size: 21px">zmling@scut.edu.cn</span></span></a><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span><span style=";font-family:'MS Mincho';font-size:21px"></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">以上通知内容，请各院（系）教务员及有关人员认真学习和理解。若有疑问，请及时与</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">本科生院</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">教务科/</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">国际校区教学事务办公室</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">联系（电话： 87110736，</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">81182790</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">,</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">81181639）。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px"> </span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px"></span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://110.65.10.251:8089/zhinan/res/cms/lib/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;"/><a href="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/file/20250926/1758870273925095337.doc" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" title="附件1：2019-2024级通识教育课程学分要求.doc">附件1：2019-2024级通识教育课程学分要求.doc</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://110.65.10.251:8089/zhinan/res/cms/lib/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;"/><a href="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/file/20250926/1758870279501043432.doc" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" title="附件2：《2026届毕业班各专业培养方案学分要求明细表》.doc">附件2：《2026届毕业班各专业培养方案学分要求明细表》.doc</a></p><p style=